| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3865 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1c69b9a4-5bb7-529e-9875-a3709f78106f"
